Requirements Are:-
------------------

              Any Classic Amiga, SEE TEXT BELOW.
              Standard Kickstart 2.0x or better.
              Workbench 1.3x is used in this part.
              PAR: Device installed.
              A copy of AmigaBASIC and related files.
              AND, how to use AmigaBASIC on a normal A1200 from AMINET:-

              <http://main.aminet.net/dev/basic/AmigaBASIC-Info.lha>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

IF you want to use ARexx instead then ignore AmigaBASIC and Workbench 1.3x
and use OS2.0x or greater and some test software from:-

              <http://main.aminet.net/dev/src/PAR_ARexx.lha>

Ensure RexxMast is running, and RX is in the path.

